snippet.title: Haunted Record - Trailer
snippet.description:
Haunted Record is a 20 minute point-and-click story about a mysterious ghost and an even more mysterious journalist.
Explore an abandoned home, talk to a confused ghost, find clues to figure out what happened, and leave with even more questions.

Releases on 23/07/2024
